title: Jerky Boyz Chicken Jerky Recalls Chicken Jerky Products due to Possible Processing Deviation
summary: WASHINGTON, Oct. 11, 2018 Jerky Boyz Chicken Jerky, a Pigeon Forge, Tenn. establishment, is recalling approximately 23 pounds of ready-to-eat chicken jerky products due to a processing deviation that may have led to underprocessing of products, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection...
